==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Tonga
<hw>Ton"ga</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Med.)</fld> <def>A
drug useful in neuralgia, derived from a Fijian plant supposed to be of
the aroid genus <gen>Epipremnum</gen>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Tonga</ent>⟦br⟧

==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Tonga
<hw>Ton"ga</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Hind.
<ets>t⟦amac⟧ng⟦amac⟧</ets>, Skr. <ets>tama⟦ndot⟧gaka</ets>.]</ety>
<def>A kind of light two-wheeled vehicle, usually for four persons,
drawn by ponies or bullocks.</def> <mark>[India]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>Webster 1913 Suppl.</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Tongkang</ent>⟦br⟧
